title: Total United States vehicles entering in Canada 2018
summary: The graph shows the trend of the Total Number of United States States vehicles to Canada during the year 2018 .
The Number drops between January and February shows the minimum value in February .
From February on it increases and shows the maximum value in August .
gold: The graph indicates the entering vehicles from the united states in canada in the year of 2018 . It is noticeable that the number is rising sharply by the middle of the year , reaching a maximum of 1200000 in August . Then the value is strong again until the end of the year .
